Google Webmaster Tool
=======================
Register website using one of the methods available


What to do be with Google Webmaster Tool
=========================================
1. HTML Improvements
Correct Meta description and Title tag
Webmaster Tools > Search Appearance > HTML Improvements

2. Detecting malwares
Webmaster Tools > Security Issues

3. Seach query analysis
Webmaster Tools > Search Traffic > Search Queries > Top Queries
a. Limit data to a most recent day to get the recent keywords used by visitors. This will help in getting good 
keywords/topics for the website that are not fully optimized.
b. Analyse the query data to get list of new keywords. Use Adwords to get keyword volume.

Ref:
http://searchenginewatch.com/article/2273660/How-to-Use-Google-Webmaster-Tools-to-Maximize-Your-SEO-Campaign
https://blog.kissmetrics.com/google-webmaster-tools-2012/
To get a keyword search volume
https://adwords.google.com/ko/KeywordPlanner/Home?__u=4849752880&__c=9752018410
